%N A397682 Decimal expansion of Integral_{x=0..1} arctan(x)^4 dx.
%F A397682 Equals Pi^4/256 - 9*Pi*zeta(3)/64 + Pi^3*log(2)/32 - 3*Pi^2*G/8 + (psi'''(1/4) - psi'''(3/4))/512, where G is Catalan's constant (A006752), and psi'''(x) is the third derivative of the digamma function.
%e A397682 0.097825961869345019483768575045683474739375472469643...
%t A397682 RealDigits[Pi^4/256 - 9*Pi*Zeta[3]/64 + Pi^3*Log[2]/32 - 3*Pi^2*Catalan/8 + (PolyGamma[3, 1/4] - PolyGamma[3, 3/4])/512, 10, 120, -1][[1]]
%t A397682 (* Alternative: *)
%t A397682 RealDigits[Re[Integrate[ArcTan[x]^4, {x, 0, 1}]], 10, 120, -1][[1]]
%o A397682 (PARI) Pi^4/256 - 9*Pi*zeta(3)/64 + Pi^3*log(2)/32 - 3*Pi^2*Catalan/8 + (psi'''(1/4) - psi'''(3/4))/512
%Y A397682 Cf. A002162, A002117, A006752, A390074, A390075.
%Y A397682 Integral_{x=0..1} arctan(x)^m dx: 196521 (m=1), A397680 (m=2), A397681 (m=3), this constant (m=4).
